#import #organization   #Free_City_of_Haven #type-family
# Rand Family

The Rands are considered upstarts, having burst upon the Haven financial scene only a decade ago; their flamboyant rise to the near top of the banking pile has made them many enemies, but the three Rand brothers appear unconcerned with others' opinions of them - they are, purely and simply, out to make as much money as they can. 

The head of the group is the eldest brother, [[Person/Kruegger Rand|Kruegger]], the most money-wise of the three and under his direction the family's fortunes have increased many fold. The other two, [[Person/Sberri Rand|Sberri Rand]] and [[Person/Zalle Rand|Zalle Rand]], are good investors, one in land, the other in commodities for export, but neither has the management skill displayed by [[Person/Kruegger Rand|Kruegger]]. 

The three share an estate in [[Settlement/The Glens|The Glens]] and only [[Person/Zalle Rand|Zalle]] is wed, to [[person/Eezie Rand|Eezie Rand]] (nee [[Organization/Families/Hofstra Family|Hofstra]], which has prompted rumors of a possible merger between two of the largest fortunes in Haven.

![[DnDLine.png]]

**Family Leader:** [[Person/Kruegger Rand|Kruegger Rand]]

